episodes.title: Victory Lobster
episodes.summary:
This week on YKWD: Bobby's out of town, but we have a hilarious episode hosted by Mike Brown and Brandon Collins (both from the Comedy Outliers Podcast). Guests: Jon Laster, Sydnee Washington, and Gordon Baker Bone. On this super last-minute Black History Month commemoration, we devote some time to all things 'hood. Things are kept real, "fo sho". Plus, a hilarious call in from Bobby Kelly! Watch / Listen and enjoy!

www.RiotCast.com

episodes.title: Shiny Helmet
episodes.summary:
This week on YKWD: We have Mike Cannon, Wendi Starling, and Myq Kaplan! Bobby and Myq share hilarious stories from their times at the Comedy Studio, Wendi shows us how she keeps it real, and Mike comes back on the show to check on the fleshlight he gifted Bobby years ago! Watch / Listen and enjoy!

episodes.title: Butt, Stomach, or Swallow
episodes.summary:
This week on YKWD: We have Luis J Gomez, Dan Soder, and Rosebud Baker! Deepu and Lauren exchange passive aggressive love letters, we take a call from someone trying to call another podcast, and we discuss the viability of semen-infused foods. Watch / Listen and enjoy!

episodes.title: A Tahiti 10
episodes.summary: This week on YKWD: We have Shuli, Jared Freid, and Liza Treyger! We talk about the minutiae of Jewish summer camps, take a closer look at the Arnold Schwarzenegger scandal, and evaluate how well George Lopez handled a heckler! Watch / Listen and enjoy!

episodes.title: A Lil Confused
episodes.summary:
This week on YKWD: Paul Virzi hosts with Luchana Gatica and Yannis Pappas! Luchana tells us of a strange first date that never should have worked out. We talk about about Boy Scouts finally letting a trans person into their ranks. We also do hysterical and filthy Aaron Berg impressions! Plus so much more! Enjoy!

episodes.title: L. Ron Tubbard
episodes.summary:
This week on YKWD: We have Anthony Cumia, Casey Balsham, and Paul Virzi! We talk about Lauren performing stand up on Paid or Pain, #womensmarch, and the less-than-glamorous world of owning a primitive dog! Watch/Listen and enjoy!

episodes.title: Provocateur
episodes.summary:
This week on YKWD: we have Tim Dillon, Carmen Lynch, and Joe Machi! We talk about legally running over protestors, smart people contracting herpes, and the prophet named Steve Harvey! Watch / Listen and enjoy!

episodes.title: No D for a Year
episodes.summary: This Week on YKWD: We have Joe List, Yamaneika Saunders, and Mike Feeney! We talk about certain comics owning certain references, Meryl Streep and Trump going at it, and the plight of the African American wig! Watch / Listen and enjoy!

episodes.title: The Big Enis
episodes.summary:
This week on YKWD: We have Sean Donnelly and Mark Normand! We discuss some listener-suggested great moments from the past year, belittle Mark's home town, and wax poetic about deep sea creatures found in the Baltic Sea (it's funnier than that sounds) . Watch / Listen and enjoy!

episodes.title: Ride the Vein
episodes.summary: This week on YKWD: We have Marina Franklin, Aaron Berg, Derek Gaines and Christian Polanco! We discuss an appalling video (New Years Resolutions for White Guys) that MTV has since taken down, field some of the best calls we've had all year, and choose between Marina's handjob story and Bob's trip to the rooftop! Watch / Listen and enjoy!
